{
  "texts": [
    "In phase (a), generative models (CVAE) are frozen.",
    "The attention module and classification module are updated with classification-based discriminant loss Ld, representationbased reconstruction loss Lre, and regularized loss Lguide.",
    "In phase (b), the attention and classification modules are frozen.",
    "CVAE is trained to use losses to reconstruct representations of frames with different values.",
    "Nguyen et al. (2018) proposed a new weakly supervised learning method in 2018."
  ]
}